has something to do with me.
他认为食物短缺是我的错

916
00:56:53,590 --> 00:56:57,250
Do you not understand that we can
only survive here when we're in harmony?
我们只有和谐共处才能生存下去

917
00:56:57,420 --> 00:57:00,650
