did not cause it, then what did?
不是你们造成的，会是什么？

923
00:57:14,940 --> 00:57:17,240
I think it comes from outside.
Way beyond the ice.
有外力因素，在冰原之外

924
00:57:17,410 --> 00:57:19,740
There are things out there,
things we don't understand.
那里有一种我们不了解的生物

925
00:57:19,910 --> 00:57:21,570
- Mysteries.
- Mind-boggling mysteries.
- 那是个谜
- 天大的谜团

926
00:57:21,750 --> 00:57:23,150
- Mystic beings.
- Yeah, aliens.
- 神秘生物
- 对，外星怪客

927
00:57:23,320 --> 00:57:24,940
- He's mad.
- No, aliens.
- 他疯了
- 不，是外星怪客

928
00:57:25,120 --> 00:57:26,780
- I hear they're smart.
- He's insane.
- 我听说他们很聪明
- 他疯了！

929
00:57:26,950 --> 00:57:29,580
No, they might be smarter than all of us.
Who knows?
不，他们可能比我们都聪明

930
00:57:29,750 --> 00:57:32,150
