Don't worry, tall guy.
My father also called me a pitiful loser.
别担心，高个子
我爸也说我是没用的肉脚

993
01:00:59,950 --> 01:01:01,080
Look how I turn out.
看看我现在，我还不是好好的

994
01:01:01,260 --> 01:01:02,450
You're not helping, Ramon.
你在帮倒忙，雷蒙

995
01:01:02,620 --> 01:01:06,320
He gonna be okay. All he gotta do
is find out what happened to the fish.
他不会有事的
只要查清楚鱼都去哪了就好办了

996
