- 不要吧！

1004
01:01:26,480 --> 01:01:28,810
"Can anybody find me"...
# 有谁可以为我…

1005
01:01:29,220 --> 01:01:31,880
- You're cracking the ice!
- Avalanche!
- 冰都被你震裂了
- 是雪崩！

1006
01:01:32,050 --> 01:01:33,710
Yes, okay. Thank you.
多谢了

1007
01:01:44,130 --> 01:01:47,030
Lovelace. You there?
爱拉斯，你在吗？

1008
01:01:47,200 --> 01:01:49,330
Lovelace!
爱拉斯！

1009
01:01:52,210 --> 01:01:54,000
Lovelace.
爱拉斯

1010
01:01:59,050 --> 01:02:00,670
Lovelace?
爱拉斯？

1011
01:02:00,850 --> 01:02:02,180
Is this a bad time?
时机好像不太对喔

1012
01:02:02,350 --> 01:02:04,280
I know we don't have
an appointment, but...
我知道我们没预约…

1013
01:02:04,450 --> 01:02:06,580
Just one question and
I want a straight answer.
只有一个问题，我要你老实回答

1014
01:02:06,750 --> 01:02:08,350
Where do I find the mystic beings?
到哪里可以找到奥秘之神？

1015
01:02:11,190 --> 01:02:13,180
Why don't he speak?
他怎么不说话？

1016
01:02:15,200 --> 01:02:17,820
Lovelace, you okay?
爱拉斯，你没事吧？

1017
01:02:19,300 --> 01:02:22,500
- Boy, he's possessed.
- It's a seizure! It's a seizure!
- 他中邪了
- 是癫痫，癫痫！

1018
01:02:22,670 --> 01:02:24,140
- Open the beak.
- Grab his tongue.
- 把嘴掰开
- 拉出他的舌头

1019
01:02:24,310 --> 01:02:26,900
He's choking. That thing
around his neck, it's too tight.
他脖子上的东西勒太紧了

1020
01:02:27,070 --> 01:02:29,700
- Well, why didn't you say so?
- On three.
- 嘿，你怎么不早说
- 听我数到三

1021
01:02:29,880 --> 01:02:34,140
Stop! Listen! No! Amigos! Amigos! Stop!
- 一、二、三、四！
- 住手，大伙儿，住手！

1022
01:02:34,320 --> 01:02:36,310
- What?
- You're hurting him.
- 干嘛？
- 你们伤到他了

1023
01:02:38,390 --> 01:02:39,850
Any better?
有没有好一点？

1024
01:02:40,020 --> 01:02:42,550
Lovelace, how did you get
that thing around your neck?
你脖子上的东西是怎么来的？

1025
01:02:42,720 --> 01:02:46,060
- It was bestowed on him.
- By the mystic beings.
- 神赐给他的
- 奥秘之神

1026
01:02:46,230 --> 01:02:48,390
- They didn't bestow it?
- No.
- 不是吗？
- 不是

1027
01:02:48,560 --> 01:02:51,550
Oh, come on, he don't know
what he's saying.
拜托，他脑袋糊涂了

1028
01:02:51,730 --> 01:02:54,720
You were swimming
and it just got caught around your neck.
你在游泳，结果被那玩意套住？

1029
01:02:54,900 --> 01:02:57,800
Oh, no way. He the guru.
不可能，他是大师

1030
01:02:58,810 --> 01:03:02,000
Lovelace, did you ever actually meet
a mystic being?
爱拉斯，你见过奥秘之神吗？

1031
01:03:02,740 --> 01:03:04,370
Officially?
真的吗？

1032
01:03:05,850 --> 01:03:06,840
No.
没有

1033
01:03:07,010 --> 01:03:08,950
I knew it! It's all a lie.
我就知道，他在骗人

1034
01:03:09,120 --> 01:03:10,980
But this belongs to someone.
这一定属于某个人

1035
01:03:11,150 --> 01:03:13,850
If we could find them,
I bet you they could take it off.
要是能找到他们，我敢肯定他们能把它拿下来

1036
01:03:14,250 --> 01:03:18,490
Show me where you found it. I'm sure
they could help us. You and me both.
告诉我你在哪里被套住的
我相信他们会帮助我们的，你和我

1037
01:03:21,330 --> 01:03:23,230
Two words, three syllables.
两个单词，三个音节

1038
01:03:23,400 --> 01:03:25,190
- What is it?
- You're dying?
- 到底是什么？
- 你快挂了？

1039
01:03:25,370 --> 01:03:29,060
No, no, wait. Past, past, your past life.
不对，过去，你的过去…

1040
01:03:29,240 --> 01:03:30,830
You're passing gas.
你在放屁

1041
01:03:32,240 --> 01:03:34,230
Now he thinks he's an elephant seal.
不对，他说他是海象

1042
01:03:34,410 --> 01:03:36,340
No, no, no. Go over the mountains.
不对，翻越那座山

1043
01:03:36,510 --> 01:03:39,450
- Go over the mountains!
- Through the land of the elephant seals.
- 翻越那座山
- 前往海象王国

1044
01:03:39,610 --> 01:03:44,210
- Beyond the land of the elephant seals.
- Beyond the land of the elephant seals!
- 越过海象王国
- 答对了！

1045
01:03:55,160 --> 01:03:57,320
- Wait.
- What?
- 等等
- 什么？

1046
01:03:58,230 --> 01:04:00,220
I hear voices.
我听到声音

1047
01:04:00,400 --> 01:04:02,060
- There is a voice.
- Where?
- 传来一个声音
- 哪里？

1048
01:04:02,240 --> 01:04:05,800
- There's a little voice on the wind.
- Mumble!
- 风中传来微弱的叫声
- 曼波！

1049
01:04:05,970 --> 01:04:07,270
- "Mambo"?
- "Mambo"?
- “曼波”？
- “曼波”？

1050
01:04:07,440 --> 01:04:08,870
- Listen.
- Mumble Happy Feet.
- 听
- 快乐大脚，曼波

1051
01:04:09,410 --> 01:04:10,640
- Gloria?
- Gloria!
- 葛露亚？
- 葛露亚！

1052
01:04:10,810 --> 01:04:11,800
Gloria?
葛露亚？

1053
01:04:11,980 --> 01:04:14,500
Hey, you got a stalker.
She's obsessed with you, man.
嘿，来了个追随者
她很崇拜你呦！

1054
01:04:18,120 --> 01:04:20,590
I can't believe it's you.
我不敢相信是你

1055
01:04:20,750 --> 01:04:22,810
Of course it's me.
当然是我了

1056
01:04:24,120 --> 01:04:25,820
What are you doing here?
你跑来做什么？

1057
01:04:25,990 --> 01:04:29,190
All the love in the world can't be gone
# 世界的爱不会消失

1058
01:04:29,360 --> 01:04:33,230
All the need to be loved can't be wrong
# 需要爱的人绝对不会错

1059
01:04:33,400 --> 01:04:36,130
- Oh, my.
- So which way, twinkletoes?
- 噢，天哪
- 往哪走，舞王？

1060
01:04:36,300 --> 01:04:39,670
No, no, no. If you come,
you may never get back home.
不行，你跟我走就回不了家

1061
01:04:39,840 --> 01:04:41,210
Fine by me.
我无所谓

1062
01:04:41,380 --> 01:04:46,840
Gloria, you have a life back there.
I don't. I mean, we don't. Not out here.
葛露亚，你过得好好的，我不一样
我们不能在这里过日子

1063
01:04:47,010 --> 01:04:50,110
How can we keep an egg safe?
That's if we ever had an egg.
怎么保护蛋？如果要生蛋的话

1064
01:04:50,280 --> 01:04:52,880
Well, I don't need an egg to be happy.
我不必生蛋就很快乐

1065
01:04:53,050 --> 01:04:57,080
You say that now, but what about later
when all your friends have eggs?
你现在说的容易
等你朋友都生了你就会后悔

1066
01:04:58,460 --> 01:04:59,690
Then I'll have you.
我有你就好

1067
01:05:01,130 --> 01:05:04,530
Now he's going to pledge
his soul forever.
立下山盟海誓的机会来了

1068
01:05:04,700 --> 01:05:05,820
- Gloria.
- Here it comes.
- 葛露亚
- 他要说了

1069
01:05:06,000 --> 01:05:12,930
I'm a particular kind of guy,
the kind of guy who needs his own space.
我是个怪胎
我需要自己的空间

1070
01:05:13,210 --> 01:05:15,070
It's not you, it's me.
你没问题，是我的错

1071
01:05:15,240 --> 01:05:17,680
I'm just not up for a serious relationship
right now.
我还没准备认真谈感情

1072
01:05:17,850 --> 01:05:21,180
What he's trying to do now
is he's pushing her away. Let's watch.
他想要赶她回家，好戏上场啰

1073
01:05:21,350 --> 01:05:24,840
No matter what you say or do,
you're stuck with me.
不管你怎么说我都跟定你了

1074
01:05:25,020 --> 01:05:28,110
Oh, come on. As if you're not
totally thrilled that I'm here.
少装了，你看到我很高兴

1075
01:05:28,290 --> 01:05:31,750
- Now she got him on the ropes.
- See, right there is your problem.
- 她把他逼到死角
- 瞧，这就是你的问题

1076
01:05:31,930 --> 01:05:33,830
You think you're irresistible, don't you?
你自以为是万人迷，对吧？

1077
01:05:33,990 --> 01:05:36,330
I don't care where you're from,
that's got to hurt.
这种话真伤人

1078
01:05:36,500 --> 01:05:39,230
- Excuse me?
- Gloria's so gorgeous, Gloria's so talented.
- 你说什么？
- 葛露亚美若天仙，才华洋溢

1079
01:05:39,400 --> 01:05:40,390
What?
什么？

1080
01:05:40,570 --> 01:05:42,970
Just because
you can hit a few high notes.
会飚高音有什么了不起

1081
01:05:43,140 --> 01:05:45,260
You got a problem with my singing?
你对我的歌声有意见？

1082
01:05:45,440 --> 01:05:47,670
No, it's perfectly fine.
我觉得还好？

1083
01:05:47,840 --> 01:05:49,710
- "Fine"?
- Lf you like that sort of thing.
- 还好？
- 如果你喜欢这样赞美你的话

1084
01:05:49,880 --> 01:05:52,470
- It's a little Nana Tootsie for my taste.
- What?
- 我觉得你的曲风太幼稚了
- 什么？

1085
01:05:52,650 --> 01:05:54,770
You know, showy, flashy, froufrou.
没品味，太煽情，太浮华了

1086
01:05:54,950 --> 01:05:56,440
- "Froufrou"?
- That's right.
- 太浮华了？
- 没错

1087
01:05:56,620 --> 01:06:00,750
Coming from someone who thinks it's cool
to jig up and down really fast on the spot...
你只会用两只脚乱跳乱抖

1088
01:06:00,920 --> 01:06:03,190
...like some twitchy idiot.
像个抽筋的小丑

1089
01:06:06,960 --> 01:06:09,590
You stubborn, hippity-hoppity fool!
固执又可恶的讨厌鬼

1090
01:06:09,760 --> 01:06:11,630
Right back at you.
骂得好

1091
01:06:21,980 --> 01:06:24,470
Amigo, that was a good thing you do.
你这么做是为她好

1092
01:06:24,650 --> 01:06:26,910
She is going to be so much better off
without you.
她离开你会过更好的生活

1093
01:06:27,080 --> 01:06:30,210
She is going to find a good, steady guy
to comfort her...
她会去找一个善良的，站得稳的家伙来安慰她

1094
01:06:30,380 --> 01:06:33,580
...and love her up real good
and raise a big family.
真心爱她，组织大家庭

1095
01:06:33,750 --> 01:06:35,980
- Ramon.
- And then she's going to let herself go...
- 雷蒙
- 然后她会变成黄脸婆…

1096
01:06:36,160 --> 01:06:39,280
Ramon. He's hurting. He's hurting bad.
雷蒙
他很心痛，痛到不行

1097
01:06:39,460 --> 01:06:44,120
Oh, listen, listen, don't hold it in
or you explode. You got to let it out.
听好，别强忍，不然会爆炸

1098
01:06:44,300 --> 01:06:46,990
You just let it out. You let it out.
你要发泄出来，发泄出来吧

1099
01:06:47,170 --> 01:06:50,030
Everybody, turn away for a moment.
大伙儿，转过去

1100
01:06:50,200 --> 01:06:52,500
If she leave him now
# 她离开他

1101
01:06:52,670 --> 01:06:57,870
She take away the biggest part of him
# 带走他的一部分

1102
01:07:00,250 --> 01:07:02,180
Don't, baby, please, don't go
# 宝贝，请不要走

1103
01:07:02,350 --> 01:07:04,210
Please, guys.
拜托，伙计们

1104
01:07:04,380 --> 01:07:06,380
No more singing.
不要再唱了

1105
01:07:16,960 --> 01:07:19,630
Then she say to me, "Enough,
you are making me nauseous."
她跟我说：“你让我好想吐”

1106
01:07:19,800 --> 01:07:23,530
So I become silent, almost moody,
and you know what she says?
我就生闷气不说话
你知道她怎么说？

1107
01:07:23,700 --> 01:07:25,760
"You never share. You got to let it out."
“你从来不说，你要发泄出来”

1108
01:07:25,940 --> 01:07:28,700
- Ramon, come on.
- Let it out. Let it out.
- 雷蒙，够了
- 发泄出来

1109
01:07:28,880 --> 01:07:30,310
Stop it! Let it go.
够了

1110
01:07:30,480 --> 01:07:34,140
- I never had a good relationship in my life.
- Give him a hug. Give him a hug.
- 我这辈子不曾有过美好恋情
- 抱抱他

1111
01:07:34,310 --> 01:07:35,540
- I let it out!
- There we go.
- 我发泄出来了
- 开始了

1112
01:07:35,720 --> 01:07:38,280
- I let it out.
- I know. Get over it.
- 我发泄出来了
- 我知道，别再发泄了

1113
01:07:38,450 --> 01:07:41,250
- Can you keep going?
- Yeah.
- 你还能走吗？
- 可以啊

1114
01:07:41,420 --> 01:07:44,620
- What's that smell?
- It wasrt me.
- 什么味道？
- 不是我

1115
01:07:45,760 --> 01:07:49,530
Hey, Fluffy, we're following you.
Get up here.
嘿，大毛球，是你在带路，快上来

1116
01:07:57,670 --> 01:08:01,730
So these elephant seals,
they're not penguin eaters, are they?
这些海象
他们不吃企鹅，对吧？

1117
01:08:01,910 --> 01:08:04,310
I don't know.
I believe they are herbivores.
不知道，他们是食草动物

1118
01:08:04,480 --> 01:08:06,340
- What?
- You know, kelp-suckers.
- 什么？
- 我是说，他们只吃海藻

1119
01:08:06,510 --> 01:08:08,850
Here we go, Lovelace. Come on.
来吧，爱拉斯，跳

1120
01:08:10,520 --> 01:08:12,380
Jump in time. Jump in time.
该跳啰，该跳啰

1121
01:08:12,550 --> 01:08:15,320
- Okay, let's do it.
- Okay, okay, okay. Ready?
- 好了，我们走吧
- 好、好、好了吗？

1122
01:08:18,530 --> 01:08:20,930
I can do this. I can do this.
I got to trick myself.
我可以的…我要骗自己做得到

1123
01:08:21,090 --> 01:08:22,990
Boy, look at that. What?
你看，那是什么？

1124
01:08:38,950 --> 01:08:43,510
You blokes better be lost,
because trespassing's a crime.
你们最好快滚，擅闯民宅是犯罪

1125
01:08:43,680 --> 01:08:47,680
- We're just passing through.
- Yeah. We're with him.
- 我们只是路过
- 对，他带我们来的

1126
01:08:48,290 --> 01:08:50,760
You wouldn't be heading
over them distant hills...
你们该不会想越过高山……

1127
01:08:50,920 --> 01:08:52,860
...and through the blizzard country?
……再穿过冰天雪地吧？

1128
01:08:53,030 --> 01:08:55,820
If it's the only way
to the forbidden shore, yeah.
这样才能抵达禁忌彼岸

1129
01:08:56,000 --> 01:08:57,190
Crikey.
了不起

1130
01:08:57,360 --> 01:09:00,860
You might come face to face
with an annihilator.
你们可能会面对面碰上终极杀手

1131
01:09:01,030 --> 01:09:02,060
An alien annihilator?
终极杀手？

1132
01:09:02,240 --> 01:09:05,170
Too right. Cut you up
as soon as look at you.
没错，一见到你就会宰了你

1133
01:09:05,340 --> 01:09:08,370
Waste every living thing in their path.
见一个杀一个

1134
01:09:08,540 --> 01:09:10,200
Could they be annihilating the fish?
鱼也是他们杀的吗？

1135
01:09:10,380 --> 01:09:11,970
Every living thing.
只要是活的都逃不了

1136
01:09:12,150 --> 01:09:14,610
Merciless, mate. Merciless.
冷血无情，毫不留情

1137
01:09:14,780 --> 01:09:17,080
Even if you're a whopping great whale...
即使你是庞大的巨鲸……

1138
01:09:17,250 --> 01:09:19,910
...they drag your sorry carcass ashore...
他们照样把你拖到岸上

1139
01:09:20,090 --> 01:09:25,790
...dice you up, melt you down,
and turn you into fun food.
……切成块，化成汤
变为他们的美味大餐……

1140
01:09:25,960 --> 01:09:28,220
One day you're a big old whale...
前一刻你还是一头巨鲸……

1141
01:09:28,400 --> 01:09:30,690
...next minute...
……后一刻……

1142
01:09:30,860 --> 01:09:32,260
...fun food.
……就变成美味大餐了

1143
01:09:32,430 --> 01:09:33,870
Someone's gotta stop them.
一定要有人阻止他们

1144
01:09:34,030 --> 01:09:36,530
Oh, yeah? What's gonna be
your approach?
是吗？你要怎么做？

1145
01:09:36,700 --> 01:09:38,730
If I could just talk to them.
我可以找他们谈

1146
01:09:38,910 --> 01:09:40,400
Appeal to their better nature.
激起他们的同情心

1147
01:09:40,570 --> 01:09:41,560
Beauty.
漂亮

1148
01:09:41,740 --> 01:09:47,340
When that crafty little trick pays off,
you be sure to let us know, won't you?
成功了记得要通知我们哦

1149
01:09:47,510 --> 01:09:50,380
All right, Lovelace, let's go.
好吧，爱拉斯，我们走

1150
01:09:52,620 --> 01:09:54,710
See you, Lovelace.
再见，爱拉斯

1151
01:09:57,160 --> 01:09:59,590
Your funeral, mate.
那边会是你的墓地，伙计

1152
01:10:47,410 --> 01:10:49,970
Oh, man!
噢，天

1153
01:10:51,010 --> 01:10:53,740
- Push tight.
- Okay.
- 用力推啊
- 好

1154
01:11:08,400 --> 01:11:10,560
Come on, guys. Let's do it.
来啊，伙计们，加油！

1155
01:11:10,730 --> 01:11:14,630
You can do it. Come on, push!
你们能行的，快点，推啊

1156
01:11:58,880 --> 01:12:00,900
What's that noise?
什么声音？

1157
01:12:02,450 --> 01:12:03,640
There's no noise.
没听见啊

1158
01:12:03,820 --> 01:12:06,380
- No gasping. No wheezing.
- Where's Lovelace?
- 没有喘气，也没有呼吸
- 爱拉斯呢？

1159
01:12:08,460 --> 01:12:13,220
Sometimes a brave penguin
will just slip away to die.
有时候勇敢的企鹅会躲起来等死

1160
01:12:13,390 --> 01:12:15,330
Do you think he went to a happy place?
他上了天堂吗？

1161
01:12:15,500 --> 01:12:19,090
- Probably.
- No, no. I think he went this way.
- 有可能
- 不，他往这边走了

1162
01:12:31,140 --> 01:12:33,640
Come on. Let's go.
来吧，我们走

1163
01:12:50,230 --> 01:12:52,130
Lovelace!
爱拉斯！

1164
01:12:53,300 --> 01:12:55,790
Lovelace!
爱拉斯！

1165
01:13:01,840 --> 01:13:03,670
Hello?
哈罗！

1166
01:13:05,080 --> 01:13:06,480
Is there anyone there?
有人吗？

1167
01:13:06,650 --> 01:13:10,240
- No... No need to shout.
- Somebody might hear you.
- 别叫这么大声
- 会被人听见

1168
01:13:15,890 --> 01:13:17,650
His feet don't look too good.
他的脚好像有点跛

1169
01:13:17,820 --> 01:13:20,420
- He rested here.
- Now he's on his belly!
- 他在这里休息
- 现在是用爬的

1170
01:13:20,590 --> 01:13:23,150
- No, this way.
- You don't want to know what he did here.
- 他往这边去了
- 你不会想知道他在干嘛

1171
01:13:23,330 --> 01:13:25,560
- You're right.
- There he is. Lovelace!
- 你说得对
- 他在那里，爱拉斯！

1172
01:13:25,730 --> 01:13:29,030
- All right! Lovelace!
- Lovelace!
- 太好了，爱拉斯！
- 爱拉斯！

1173
01:13:31,810 --> 01:13:33,570
- Oh, look at Lovelace.
- We're here.
- 看看爱拉斯
- 我们来了

1174
01:13:33,740 --> 01:13:37,300
- Are you okay?
- Come on, man. Hang in there, buddy.
- 你没事吧？
- 加油，撑下去，伙计

1175
01:13:38,180 --> 01:13:39,810
What is it?
那是什么？

1176
01:13:39,980 --> 01:13:43,250
Oh, look. There's one for everyone.
瞧，大家都有份

1177
01:13:43,420 --> 01:13:45,940
Hang in there, Lovelace.
I know they're here somewhere.
撑下去，他们就在附近

1178
01:13:46,120 --> 01:13:48,640
- Why would they leave all this behind?
- I don't know.
- 他们干嘛丢下这些？
- 不知道

1179
01:13:49,660 --> 01:13:50,650
Hey.
嘿

1180
01:13:50,820 --> 01:13:53,090
- Tell them we come in peace.
- We come in peace!
- 快说我们爱好和平
- 我们爱好和平

1181
01:13:53,260 --> 01:13:54,780
- Lovelace.
- Lovelace.
- 爱拉斯
- 爱拉斯

1182
01:13:54,960 --> 01:13:56,430
- Lovelace.
- Oh, buddy, come on.
- 爱拉斯
- 哦，伙计，坚持住

1183
01:13:56,600 --> 01:13:58,660
- Are you okay?
- Hang in there, buddy.
- 你没事吧？
- 坚持住，伙计

1184
01:14:01,270 --> 01:14:03,740
- Oh, that's not good.
- Stay calm.
- 大事不妙
- 冷静点

1185
01:14:03,900 --> 01:14:05,200
- Stay calm.
- That's not good.
- 冷静点
- 不好了

1186
01:14:05,370 --> 01:14:07,970
- Okay, don't stay calm!
- Panic!
- 糗了，冷静不了了
- 抓狂了

1187
01:14:14,680 --> 01:14:16,650
Oh, no, no!
糟了！

1188
01:14:18,690 --> 01:14:21,780
- Oh, they're making us appe-teasers.
- They're appe-teasing us!
- 他们把我们当点心
- 他们在耍我们

1189
01:14:21,960 --> 01:14:24,080
We're all gonna die.
我们死定了

1190
01:14:25,360 --> 01:14:27,220
Whatever you do, stay out of the water!
无论如何千万不要下水！

1191
01:14:27,390 --> 01:14:29,520
- Stay out of the water.
- Don't go in the water!
- 别下水
- 不要下水

1192
01:14:29,700 --> 01:14:32,390
Lovelace, don't go in the water!
爱拉斯，不要下水

1193
01:14:38,240 --> 01:14:39,760
Lovelace, hang in there!
爱拉斯，坚持住！

1194
01:14:39,940 --> 01:14:41,840
Hang in there!
坚持住！

1195
01:14:43,210 --> 01:14:46,200
Get your dirty tongue off him!
把你恶心的舌头拿开！

1196
01:14:48,620 --> 01:14:50,520
No, no, no!
惨了！

1197
01:14:50,680 --> 01:14:52,150
Stay out of the water!
离水远点！

1198
01:14:52,320 --> 01:14:54,010
- Mumble!
- Mumble!
- 曼波！
- 曼波！

1199
01:15:24,280 --> 01:15:28,880
- They playing birdminton?
- No, it's a show. Dinner and a show.
- 他们在打鸟毛球吗？
- 不，这是表演，晚餐和表演

1200
01:15:32,530 --> 01:15:35,090
Lovelace!
爱拉斯！

1201
01:15:40,600 --> 01:15:42,590
Rejoice!
解脱了！

1202
01:15:51,010 --> 01:15:51,315
Lovelace!

1203
01:15:51,315 --> 01:15:52,209
爱拉斯！
Lovelace!

1204
01:15:52,380 --> 01:15:53,043
- Help!
- Reach out!
救命啊！

1205
01:15:53,043 --> 01:15:53,384
- Help!
- Reach out!

1206
01:15:53,384 --> 01:15:54,443
伸出手来！
- Help!
- Reach out!

1207
01:15:54,610 --> 01:15:56,450
Thank you, my brother, thank you!
谢谢你，兄弟，谢谢！

1208
01:16:07,430 --> 01:16:09,290
I wasrt scared! I wasrt scared!
老子不怕！

1209
01:16:10,100 --> 01:16:11,537
Oh, my beautiful brother, thank you,
thank you, thank you, thank you!
哦，我可爱的兄弟

1210
01:16:11,537 --> 01:16:11,601
Oh, my beautiful brother, thank you,
thank you, thank you, thank you!

1211
01:16:11,601 --> 01:16:14,037
谢谢，谢谢，谢谢，谢谢
Oh, my beautiful brother, thank you,
thank you, thank you, thank you!

1212
01:16:18,200 --> 01:16:21,170
- Go, Lovelace! You the man!
- Go, go, go, go, go!
- 爱拉斯！了不起！
- 加油，加油

1213
01:16:21,340 --> 01:16:23,810
Enough!
够了！

1214
01:16:23,980 --> 01:16:26,070
It's a bad day for you!
今天算你们两个倒霉！

1215
01:16:26,250 --> 01:16:28,310
You dealing with Lovelace now!
遇见我爱拉斯！

1216
01:16:28,480 --> 01:16:31,140
- And my man, Mumble, here.
- You tell them, Lovelace.
- 和我的好兄弟曼波
- 说得好，爱拉斯

1217
01:16:31,320 --> 01:16:34,080
Begone, demon fish. Adios.
给我滚，死鱼们！拜拜啦

1218
01:16:35,490 --> 01:16:37,120
That's right.
没错

1219
01:16:37,290 --> 01:16:39,050
You hightail it back to your mamas.
逃回你妈妈那里去吧

1220
01:16:39,360 --> 01:16:41,420
- How did he do that?
- Don't make me come in the water.
- 他是怎么做到的？
- 不要逼我下水

1221
01:16:41,590 --> 01:16:43,530
I'll come after your sons and daughters.
我不会放过你们的孩子

1222
01:16:43,700 --> 01:16:45,690
I'm gonna give you the bad eye.
我不会给你们好脸色的

1223
01:17:39,990 --> 01:17:41,320
A whole bunch of them.
一大堆的怪物

1224
01:17:41,490 --> 01:17:44,120
They gonna rule the world.
他们想统治世界

1225
01:17:44,290 --> 01:17:45,280
It's gotta be them.
一定就是他们了

1226
01:17:45,460 --> 01:17:48,720
- Lf it is, I don't wanna know about it.
- They don't even know we exist.
- 不管是什么我都不想知道
- 他们根本不知道我们的存在在

1227
01:17:48,900 --> 01:17:50,230
Let me tell something to you.
我告诉你

1228
01:17:50,400 --> 01:17:53,390
This is the end of the road. It's over.
你已经走到尽头了

1229
01:17:53,570 --> 01:17:56,470
You did everything penguinly possible.
你尽了最大的努力

1230
01:17:56,640 --> 01:17:59,100
- You found the aliens.
- We gonna testify to that.
- 你找到了外星怪客
- 我们会帮你作证的

1231
01:17:59,270 --> 01:18:02,640
We'll tell your whole laughing-boy nation
they were dead wrong about you.
跟那群老古板说他们看错你了

1232
01:18:02,810 --> 01:18:04,610
Now, let's all go back home. Right now.
现在我们都回家吧，赶紧走

1233
01:18:04,780 --> 01:18:06,140
Right on.
没错

1234
01:18:06,310 --> 01:18:07,900
- Could I ask a favor of you?
- Sure.
- 请你们帮个忙
- 好啊

1235
01:18:08,080 --> 01:18:10,640
- What kind of favor?
- Could you make sure Gloria's okay?
- 什么忙？
- 你们能照顾好葛露亚吗？

1236
01:18:10,820 --> 01:18:12,180
- And my ma.
- What?
- 还有我妈妈
- 什么？

1237
01:18:12,350 --> 01:18:13,940
And if you see Pa...
还有，如果看到我爸……

1238
01:18:14,120 --> 01:18:16,990
...tell him I tried.
……告诉他我尽力了

1239
01:18:17,160 --> 01:18:18,650
Okay, what you talking about?
好吧，不过你到底想说什么？

1240
01:18:18,830 --> 01:18:20,590
I'm gonna stop them taking our fish.
我要去阻止他们抓走我们的鱼

1241
01:18:20,760 --> 01:18:22,320
How you gonna do that, Mumble?
你要怎么阻止他们？曼波？

1242
01:18:24,700 --> 01:18:27,760
Adios, amigos!
再见，兄弟们！

1243
01:18:28,100 --> 01:18:29,590
Amigo! He did it.
老天！他是玩真的！

1244
01:18:53,160 --> 01:18:54,180
You believe that?
哇塞，你相信吗？

1245
01:18:54,360 --> 01:18:57,920
How we gonna tell his mama
he bring us all this way just to kill himself?
我们怎么跟他妈妈交代？
他这么大老远带我们来这里，就是为了自杀？

1246
01:18:58,100 --> 01:19:00,860
No. He didn't. Look.
不，他没自杀，看

1247
01:19:01,700 --> 01:19:03,460
He loco maniac.
他真是个疯子

1248
01:19:03,640 --> 01:19:06,570
First ever flying flipper bird.
历史上第一只会飞的企鹅

1249
01:19:06,740 --> 01:19:08,900
How tall you think that tall boy was?
你们说他勇不勇敢？

1250
01:19:09,080 --> 01:19:12,240
Who could say? Taller than anyone.
他比任何企鹅都勇敢

1251
01:19:12,410 --> 01:19:16,350
Hey, it's me, Lovelace...
嘿，是我，爱拉斯……

1252
01:19:16,520 --> 01:19:18,920
...formerly known as "guru."
……也就是以前大家所说的“大师”

1253
01:19:19,090 --> 01:19:22,080
I'm gonna be telling your story,
Happy Feet...
我会把你，快乐大脚的故事……

1254
01:19:22,260 --> 01:19:26,120
...long after you dead and gone!
……世世代代讲给子孙们听！

1255
01:19:43,140 --> 01:19:45,410
Hey! Hey!
嘿，嘿！

1256
01:20:35,560 --> 01:20:38,260
Enraged by their indifference...
怪物的冷漠激怒了曼波……

1257
01:20:38,430 --> 01:20:43,770
...he followed them long after
they were gone from his sight.
……即使走远了，曼波还是紧追不舍

1258
01:20:45,940 --> 01:20:50,170
He ventured further
than any of us had gone before...
到了我们想像不到的地方

1259
01:20:50,340 --> 01:20:54,180
...beyond all hope of return.
回家的路途遥遥无期

1260
01:20:55,110 --> 01:20:57,550
Swept up by the great currents...
他被强大的海流冲着

1261
01:20:57,720 --> 01:21:02,380
...he was carried endlessly
across vast oceans...
在茫茫大海中一直漂流

1262
01:21:02,560 --> 01:21:06,250
...to worlds unknown.
来到一个未知的世界

1263
01:22:02,550 --> 01:22:05,310
Excuse me. What is this place?
打扰一下，请问这是哪里？

1264
01:22:05,490 --> 01:22:08,480
You're in heaven, Dave. Penguin heaven.
这是天堂，企鹅的天堂

1265
01:22:08,650 --> 01:22:10,650
Is it anywhere near Emperor Land?
这里离帝企鹅的领地近吗？

1266
01:22:10,820 --> 01:22:13,620
It's wherever you want it to be.
你希望是什么就是什么

1267
01:22:14,460 --> 01:22:18,490
Try the water, Dave. It's really real.
下水试试吧，很像真的海水

1268
01:22:34,580 --> 01:22:38,950
I heard tell,
when he finally saw aliens up close...
我听说他终于近距离看到了外星怪客……

1269
01:22:39,120 --> 01:22:43,320
...they were just as the skua
had described.
他们的长相和贼鸥形容的一样

1270
01:22:43,490 --> 01:22:46,120
Excuse me. Why are you taking our fish?
请问，你们为什么抢走我们的鱼？

1271
01:22:46,290 --> 01:22:51,590
Big, ugly penguins without feathers
on their fat, flabby faces.
就像超丑的企鹅
只是胖脸上面没有羽毛

1272
01:22:51,760 --> 01:22:57,500
Why are you taking our fish?
You're kind of killing us out there.
你们为什么抢走我们的鱼？
你们这样会害死我们的

1273
01:22:59,870 --> 01:23:01,970
No! No, wait!
等等，别走！

1274
01:23:11,580 --> 01:23:13,550
Oh, my.
噢，天

1275
01:23:14,620 --> 01:23:18,780
Hello. Hello from Emperor Land.
Good afternoon.
哈罗，我来自帝王企鹅王国，午安

1276
01:23:18,960 --> 01:23:20,720
Why are you taking our fish?
你们为什么抢走我们的鱼？

1277
01:23:20,890 --> 01:23:25,330
I'm sure you don't mean to,
but you're causing an awful lot of grief.
也许你们不是故意的
可是你们那样会害惨我们

1278
01:23:26,330 --> 01:23:30,330
Am I not making myself clear?
I'm speaking plain penguin.
我说的话你们听懂吗？
我说的是企鹅话

1279
01:23:31,240 --> 01:23:34,800
Penguin! Don't you understand?
You're stealing our fish.
你们听不懂吗？
你们偷走我们的鱼

1280
01:23:39,080 --> 01:23:41,810
Oh, please, anyone, talk to me!
拜托，请你们回答我

1281
01:23:41,980 --> 01:23:44,210
For pity's sake, you're stealing our F-l-S...
可怜可怜我们吧
你们在偷我们的鱼……

1282
01:23:48,990 --> 01:23:53,760
After three days, he would lose his voice.
三天后他的嗓子完全沙哑

1283
01:23:53,930 --> 01:23:56,360
After three months...
三个月后……

1284
01:23:58,330 --> 01:24:02,460
...he would all but lose his mind.
他几乎快要发疯

1285
01:24:14,880 --> 01:24:17,850
So you found the fish, baby.
你找到鱼了，宝贝

1286
01:24:18,950 --> 01:24:20,610
Ma?
妈？

1287
01:24:20,790 --> 01:24:22,080
- Hi, sweetie.
- Ma.
- 嗨，亲爱的
- 妈

1288
01:24:22,260 --> 01:24:26,660
Fluffy, no matter what they say or do,
we never stopped believing in you.
毛球，不管他们怎么说，我们挺你到底

1289
01:24:26,830 --> 01:24:28,920
So you'll be back soon, right?
你很快就会回来，对吧？

1290
01:24:29,100 --> 01:24:30,720
Hey, come on. Let him eat.
嘿，别问了，让他吃吧

1291
01:24:30,900 --> 01:24:32,890
Go ahead, Dave. Don't mind us.
尽管吃，别管我们

1292
01:24:33,400 --> 01:24:34,870
But there's plenty for everyone.
但有很多鱼啊，够大家吃的

1293
01:24:35,030 --> 01:24:37,330
It's okay, sugar. We can wait.
没事的，甜心，我们可以等

1294
01:24:37,500 --> 01:24:39,330
No, no, Ma! Ma!
不，不，妈！妈！

1295
01:24:39,510 --> 01:24:42,910
There's lots here. Ma!
别走，妈，还有很多鱼

1296
01:24:46,850 --> 01:24:48,440
Ma!
妈！

1297
01:27:08,650 --> 01:27:11,350
- Kids, you gotta see this.
- He's on now.
- 孩子，这个你一定得看看
- 他又开始了

1298
01:27:33,110 --> 01:27:35,480
Hey! Hello!
嘿，大家好！

1299
01:27:37,920 --> 01:27:40,480
- Isn't that the fellow with the wacky feet?
- Looks like.
- 这不是那个脚有毛病的家伙吗？
- 看起来像

1300
01:27:40,650 --> 01:27:42,950
- What was his name?
- I thought he was dead.
- 他叫什么？
- 我以为他死了呢

1301
01:27:43,120 --> 01:27:44,520
- Everybody...
- Apparently not.
- 大家……
- 显然没死

1302
01:27:44,690 --> 01:27:47,630
Everybody, listen up! I've got big news.
大家听着！我有重大消息

1303
01:27:47,960 --> 01:27:49,950
I know who's taking the fish!
我知道鱼被谁抢走了

1304
01:27:50,130 --> 01:27:52,600
- Yeah, and they took his brain.
- It's the aliens.
- 对，然后把他的脑子也挖走了
- 是那些外星怪客

1305
01:27:52,770 --> 01:27:55,030
- I made contact with them.
- The lunatic is back.
- 我跟他们联系了
- 疯子回来了

1306
01:27:55,200 --> 01:27:57,190
The aliens are taking our fish.
是外星怪客抢走了我们的鱼

1307
01:27:57,370 --> 01:27:59,430
Someone ought to fetch
Noah and the elders.
赶快叫人去把诺亚和长老们请来

1308
01:27:59,610 --> 01:28:00,900
Hey, you.
嘿，你

1309
01:28:01,470 --> 01:28:03,030
Gloria.
葛露亚

1310
01:28:03,210 --> 01:28:05,300
Kind of weird, seeing you again.
再看到你，觉得有点怪怪的

1311
01:28:05,810 --> 01:28:06,800
Yeah.
是啊

1312
01:28:06,980 --> 01:28:09,350
- Everything cool here, baby?
- You remember Seymour.
- 没什么事吧，宝贝
- 你记得西摩吧

1313
01:28:09,520 --> 01:28:10,810
Yeah. Hi, Seymour.
当然，嗨，西摩

1314
01:28:10,980 --> 01:28:12,470
Yeah.
嗯

1315
01:28:13,790 --> 01:28:15,520
So which one is yours?
哪个是你孩子？

1316
01:28:16,760 --> 01:28:18,020
All of them.
全都是

1317
01:28:20,390 --> 01:28:24,520
This is our singing class.
He teaches rhythm. I teach the blues.
他们是我歌唱班的学生
他教韵律，我教蓝调

1318
01:28:24,700 --> 01:28:27,290
- So you're not...?
- I guess I never heard the right song.
- 你们没有…？
- 我想我还没等到属于我的那支歌

1319
01:28:27,470 --> 01:28:30,590
That's great! I didn't mean...
太好了！我不是那个意思……

1320
01:28:30,940 --> 01:28:32,530
I found out who's taking the fish.
我查出是谁偷走了鱼

1321
01:28:32,710 --> 01:28:34,830
They're big and kind of ugly,
but, Gloria...
他们很巨大，长得又丑
但是，葛露亚……

1322
01:28:35,010 --> 01:28:37,310
...the things they can do.
They're coming here.
他们很厉害，而且要来这里

1323
01:28:37,480 --> 01:28:38,600
Oh, is that so?
真的假的？

1324
01:28:38,780 --> 01:28:41,180
They'll be here soon.
I think they wanna help us.
他们就快到了，他们想帮我们

1325
01:28:41,350 --> 01:28:43,080
So now you speak with them?
那你跟他们谈过了？

1326
01:28:43,250 --> 01:28:46,450
Well, they don't speak penguin,
but they seem to respond to this.
这个，他们不说企鹅语
但他们对这个有反应

1327
01:28:46,620 --> 01:28:48,680
- What's he doing?
- You gotta be kidding me.
- 他在干嘛？
- 你玩我啊？

1328
01:28:48,850 --> 01:28:51,880
I suggest we all do it.
It really gets their attention.
我建议大家都这么做
这真的很吸引他们

1329
01:28:52,060 --> 01:28:53,390
And why would it do that?
为什么要这么做？

1330
01:28:53,560 --> 01:28:56,460
Beats me, but it works.
你问住我了，不过真的有用

1331
01:28:56,630 --> 01:28:59,500
- Hey, it's the hippity-hopper.
- Freaky feet!
- 嘿，是那个脚抽筋的家伙
- 怪胎！

1332
01:28:59,670 --> 01:29:00,650
Boys, boys...
孩子们，孩子们……

1333
01:29:00,830 --> 01:29:01,820
- Fluffy.
- Tall guy.
- 毛球
- 高个子

1334
01:29:02,000 --> 01:29:03,990
- Stretch!
- Amigo!
- 兄弟
- 朋友！

1335
01:29:07,610 --> 01:29:10,470
So you dare come back?
你还敢回来？

1336
01:29:10,780 --> 01:29:13,370
He says he's found aliens
and they're taking our fish.
他说他找到外星怪客了
是他们抢走了我们的鱼

1337
01:29:13,550 --> 01:29:16,070
He says that they're coming
and we all have to do this.
他说他们要来了
还让我们都这么做

1338
01:29:17,550 --> 01:29:21,080
There be no such thing as aliens!
这世上没有外星怪客这东西！

1339
01:29:23,190 --> 01:29:25,920
Mumble, turn around.
曼波，转过去

1340
01:29:29,060 --> 01:29:30,550
It's a disease.
是种疾病

1341
01:29:30,960 --> 01:29:32,660
Is that from them?
是他们弄的吗？？

1342
01:29:33,370 --> 01:29:37,530
Yeah. But don't be afraid.
I think it's a way to find me, that's all.
对，可是不要怕，这样他们才能找到我

1343
01:29:37,700 --> 01:29:41,400
You led them here?
You turned them on your own kind?
你带他们来，背叛你的同胞？

1344
01:29:42,210 --> 01:29:46,110
Wait a second, you just said
there's no such thing as aliens.
等等，你刚才不是说外星怪客不存在吗？

1345
01:29:48,550 --> 01:29:50,670
Well, there's not.
这个，当然没有

1346
01:29:50,850 --> 01:29:54,480
But if there were, only a traitorous fool
would bring them here.
不过万一有，只有叛徒才会带他们来这里

1347
01:29:54,650 --> 01:29:55,750
But they have to come.
他们一定要来

1348
01:29:55,920 --> 01:29:58,890
They're the ones taking our fish.
They can do something about it.
他们偷走我们的鱼，可以还给我们

1349
01:29:59,060 --> 01:30:02,550
None but the Great 'Guin
has the power to give and take away.
只有企鹅歌神才有这种神力

1350
01:30:02,730 --> 01:30:07,190
The Great 'Guin didn't put things
out of whack, the aliens did.
但是企鹅歌神没有破坏生态环境
是外星怪客干的

1351
01:30:07,770 --> 01:30:11,700
A fool returns this day
to mock our suffering.
这个白痴今天回来是来嘲笑我们的苦难

1352
01:30:11,870 --> 01:30:16,000
We are starving
and he wants us to hippity-hop.
我们在挨饿，他还要我们跳舞

1353
01:30:16,180 --> 01:30:19,110
So do we hold fast to our ways...
我们是要坚守企鹅传统

1354
01:30:19,280 --> 01:30:23,980
...or do we bend to the fetid fantasies
of a dancing fool?
还是让这个疯狂叛徒愚弄我们？

1355
01:30:32,790 --> 01:30:35,490
Say, how does that feet thing go again?
你说要怎么跳才对？

1356
01:30:35,660 --> 01:30:37,220
Yeah, show us, Mumble.
对啊，给我们演示一下，曼波

1357
01:30:38,600 --> 01:30:40,660
Oh, it's really quite easy.
哦，其实很简单

1358
01:30:40,830 --> 01:30:42,460
No, no!
不，不！

1359
01:30:42,640 --> 01:30:43,970
No, you must resist!
不要听他的！

1360
01:30:44,800 --> 01:30:46,500
That's right.
很好

1361
01:30:46,870 --> 01:30:50,240
- Pointless nonsense.
- Resist! Stand your ground!
- 没用处的胡闹
- 别听他的话，坚守立场

1362
01:30:50,410 --> 01:30:53,740
Stand your ground against this folly!
抗拒这种胡闹的行为！

1363
01:30:59,520 --> 01:31:02,580
Raise your voices, brothers.
大声吼出来，同胞们

1364
01:31:02,760 --> 01:31:06,050
Cry out in defiance of this jiggity-joggity!
喊出你们对这些小丑的蔑视！

1365
01:31:06,230 --> 01:31:08,350
Show me what you got.
秀几招来看看

1366
01:31:11,160 --> 01:31:12,890
You got it.
对极了

1367
01:31:17,440 --> 01:31:18,870
Come on.
来吧

1368
01:31:19,040 --> 01:31:20,370
Work, work it.
好，继续

1369
01:31:20,540 --> 01:31:23,630
Yes, yes! Call on the wisdoms!
很好，召唤智慧之神

1370
01:31:23,810 --> 01:31:25,540
Let the world tremble!
让大地颤抖！

1371
01:31:25,980 --> 01:31:27,840
For when all others leave...
大家都离开……

1372
01:31:28,010 --> 01:31:29,880
...we remain!
……只有我们留守！

1373
01:31:31,620 --> 01:31:33,240
Mumble! Mumble!
曼波，曼波！

1374
01:31:33,420 --> 01:31:36,220
Mama? Amigos.
妈妈？朋友们

1375
01:31:37,590 --> 01:31:40,420
- Oh, Mama.
- Oh, my boy.
- 哦，妈妈
- 哦，我的孩子

1376
01:31:40,590 --> 01:31:43,190
- My gorgeous boy.
- Oh, Mama.
- 我帅气的孩子
- 哦，妈妈

1377
01:31:43,360 --> 01:31:45,490
- Look at him.
- You're so dazzling.
- 看看他
- 你变得好帅哦

1378
01:31:45,660 --> 01:31:48,530
- Oh, Fluffy.
- We waited and waited for you.
- 哦，毛球
- 我们等了你好久

1379
01:31:48,700 --> 01:31:51,530
- Oh, yeah.
- Where's Pa?
- 噢，耶
- 爸在哪里？

1380
01:31:51,700 --> 01:31:53,970
Believe me. You don't wanna see
your deadbeat dad.
你不会想见到你老爸

1381
01:31:54,140 --> 01:31:56,200
- Your pa is sort of...
- What?
- 你爸有一点……
- 有点什么？

1382
01:31:56,380 --> 01:31:58,670
Come on, I'll show you.
来吧，我带你去看他

1383
01:32:08,050 --> 01:32:09,850
Memphis?
孟菲斯？

1384
01:32:10,890 --> 01:32:12,320
Memphis?
孟菲斯？

1385
01:32:12,490 --> 01:32:13,980
Pa?
爸？

1386
01:32:17,900 --> 01:32:19,520
Mumble?
曼波？

1387
01:32:19,700 --> 01:32:21,690
Is it truly you?
真的是你吗？

1388
01:32:21,870 --> 01:32:24,200
Every last bit of me, Pa.
完完全全是我，爸

1389
01:32:28,370 --> 01:32:30,210
I thought...
我以为……

1390
01:32:34,350 --> 01:32:35,840
Pa?
爸？

1391
01:32:39,450 --> 01:32:41,850
There ain't been one day...
打从你一出生

1392
01:32:43,820 --> 01:32:48,450
...not one day, that I done right by you.
我就没有好好对待你

1393
01:32:52,800 --> 01:32:54,820
Oh, Pa.
哦，爸

1394
01:32:55,000 --> 01:32:56,870
Dance for him, Daddy.
为他跳舞吧，孩子他爸

1395
01:32:57,040 --> 01:32:59,030
Dance with your boy.
跟孩子一起跳舞吧

1396
01:33:02,370 --> 01:33:04,770
You'll have to forgive me.
你必须原谅我

1397
01:33:05,580 --> 01:33:08,640
The music's gone clean out of me.
我完全没有节奏感

1398
01:33:10,520 --> 01:33:12,110
No, it hasn't.
不，不会的

1399
01:33:12,280 --> 01:33:16,080
It's just like singing with your body.
这就像用身体唱歌

1400
01:33:16,260 --> 01:33:18,280
Come on, baby. We can do it.
来吧，爸爸，我们一起来

1401
01:33:18,460 --> 01:33:20,020
Oh, Mama.
哦，孩子他妈

1402
01:33:20,190 --> 01:33:24,560
It's just one big old foot after the other.
两只脚来回跳动就行了

1403
01:33:29,970 --> 01:33:30,960
That's it.
就这样

1404
01:33:32,970 --> 01:33:34,800
Yeah.
是的

1405
01:33:36,180 --> 01:33:39,010
- Yeah, see?
- Well, that feels good.
- 对，没错吧？
- 嗯，感觉很好

1406
01:33:44,250 --> 01:33:47,690
You don't have to be beautiful
# 想让我激情似火

1407
01:33:48,120 --> 01:33:49,110
Yeah, Memphis.
耶，孟菲斯

1408
01:33:49,350 --> 01:33:50,980
To turn me on
# 你不必在意自己的外表

1409
01:33:51,460 --> 01:33:52,450
Daddy.
孩子他爸

1410
01:33:52,620 --> 01:33:56,650
I just need your body, baby
# 我只需要你的身体，宝贝

1411
01:33:56,830 --> 01:33:59,320
From dusk till dawn
# 从日出到日落

1412
01:34:00,530 --> 01:34:04,260
You don't have to be rich to be my girl
# 想成为我的女孩，不必多么富有

1413
01:34:04,440 --> 01:34:08,430
You don't have to be cool
To rule my world
# 想主宰我的世界，不必特意装酷

1414
01:34:08,610 --> 01:34:12,510
Ain't no particular song
I'm more compatible with
# 没有比这，更适合我的歌曲

1415
01:34:12,680 --> 01:34:17,340
I just want your extra time and your...
# 我只是需要你更多的时间，还有……

1416
01:34:37,670 --> 01:34:40,700
Holy flock!
我的老天！

1417
01:35:06,100 --> 01:35:08,530
Mommy, Mommy, Mommy.
妈呀，妈呀，妈呀

1418
01:35:45,200 --> 01:35:47,570
I think you better dance now.
我想你现在最好开始跳舞

1419
01:36:41,130 --> 01:36:43,590
First, there was just one.
Now there's thousands.
本来只有一只，现在有几千只

1420
01:36:43,760 --> 01:36:46,460
- Are they trying to tell us something?
- What's the problem?
- 他们想告诉我们什么吗？
- 问题出在哪？

1421
01:36:46,630 --> 01:36:49,430
- We're messing with their food chain.
- We've gotta do something.
- 我们破坏了他们的食物链
- 我们必须设法弥补

1422
01:36:49,600 --> 01:36:53,300
- We suggest a ban on all marine harvesting.
- Too much money. Too many jobs.
- 我建议禁止捕捉海洋生物
- 牺牲太大了

1423
01:36:55,210 --> 01:36:57,370
Why should we do anything at all?
我们为什么要帮他们？

1424
01:37:03,080 --> 01:37:06,450
They're just a bunch of flightless birds
at the bottom of the world.
它们只是这个世界的底层里
一群不会飞的笨鸟

1425
01:37:10,960 --> 01:37:13,290
I don't wanna live in a world
without penguins.
我可不想生活在没有企鹅的世界里

1426
01:37:13,460 --> 01:37:14,820
What are we gonna do about it?
我们应该怎么做？

1427
01:37:14,990 --> 01:37:16,650
Bang up the sign "No Fishing."
立起警示牌，严禁捕鱼

1428
01:37:18,430 --> 01:37:21,830
Is equal to the love...
那可是你们所做的……

1429
01:37:22,000 --> 01:37:23,400
...you make.
……爱

1430
01:37:27,470 --> 01:37:31,640
Oh, baby. Right on.
噢，宝贝，好极了

1431
01:37:44,160 --> 01:37:49,290
Looking back on when I
Was a little nappy-headed boy
# 回想过去，当我还穿着尿布

1432
01:37:52,130 --> 01:37:53,600
It's like a jungle sometimes
# 这就像是花丛

1433
01:37:53,770 --> 01:37:55,960
It makes me wonder
How I keep from going under
# 让我时而疑惑，如何抵挡这般诱惑

1434
01:37:57,900 --> 01:37:59,370
Bring it on! Go ahead!
放马过来吧！来啊！

1435
01:38:00,240 --> 01:38:04,230
Even though we sometimes
Would not get a thing
# 尽管我们有时，会一无所获

1436
01:38:04,410 --> 01:38:08,280
We were happy with
The joy the day would bring
# 但我们仍然享受，生活的快乐

1437
01:38:08,450 --> 01:38:11,610
I wish those days
Would come back once more
# 我怀念那些，逝去的时光

1438
01:38:11,780 --> 01:38:15,980
Come back those days, those days
Come back, don't go
# 回来吧 美好时光
# 回来吧 别再离去

1439
01:38:16,390 --> 01:38:19,050
Come here, babe. Come on back.
# 来吧，宝贝，回来吧

1440
01:38:19,220 --> 01:38:20,210
Come on back
# 回来吧

1441
01:38:20,390 --> 01:38:22,020
- Come on back
